author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Wonderful streaming... :_るんるん:
Also another "Super Mario Bros 35" gameplay.
We appreciate all Rushia-daitenshi's efforts for going at the top.
Also discovered something with the Right Stick control:
— At Top=Time slow
— At Left=Random
— At Right=More Coins
— At Bottom=Attacker

Note: When time is Red, goes faster, recommended the Right Stick at top (Time slow)
A Just-defense... Same as "Random" :_きゅん:

Also is a challenge for memory...
At least the 3rd place is not bad... :_ちょうちょ:

And Supaachaato Orei Time was surprising... With the echo voice, Superchats went bananas. :_ハート:
